# Implement Stream Graph Queries

Implements: [[s-443y]]

## Objective

Implement functions to query the stream relationship graph.

## Functions

```typescript
// Get child streams (forked from this stream)
function getChildStreams(streamId: string): Stream[];

// Find common ancestor commit between two streams
function findCommonAncestor(streamA: string, streamB: string): string;

// Get stream graph as tree structure from root
interface StreamNode {
  stream: Stream;
  children: StreamNode[];
  dependencies: string[];  // IDs of streams this depends on
}

function getStreamGraph(rootStreamId?: string): StreamNode | StreamNode[];
// If rootStreamId provided, returns single tree
// If not provided, returns array of root stream trees (forest)
```

## Implementation Notes

- `getChildStreams()`: Query by `parent_stream = ?`
- `findCommonAncestor()`: Use `git merge-base`
- `getStreamGraph()`: Recursive tree building from parent/child relationships

## Tests

