**healthCheck() checks:**
- Count streams and archived streams
- Count active agents (guards within last 60s)
- Find stale locks (older than 5 minutes)
- Find incomplete operations
- Find orphaned conflicts (in_progress without active rebase)
- Count pending snapshots

**startupRecovery() actions:**
1. Recover incomplete operations (reset to before_state)
2. Release stale locks (older than 5 minutes)
3. Recover orphaned conflicts (call existing recoverOrphanedConflicts)
4. Log all recovery actions

